5:
That should about do it. Now if I can
just grab a few herbs...
8: Hey, Alk! Is this fruit here safe to eat?
24:
Oh come ON! Why do I keep
messing it up?!
28: Geez! You really spooked me there!
31: When did you even set this up?!
35:
I did it all sneaky-like when you were
gathering fruit! I was careful to not
be seen!
37:
You never fall for my pranks, no
matter how hard I try...
41:
I'm just barely dodging them every
time!
44: Just... Take it easy on me, okay?
47:
Huh? No way. I'm gonna get you
good one of these days!
51:
Then I'll have something cool to
brag to Mimi and Kyoka about!
55:
So THAT'S why you've been pulling
more pranks since you reunited with
them...
59:
Hehe! You got me!
I was really surprised to see those
two all the way out here.
61:
It'd be tons of fun for us to go
exploring in another world together
someday!
65:
How are things coming along, Alk?
We've finished gathering everything
on our end.
69:
We're good here, too. We've still got
some more ingredients to gather
elsewhere, so we'd better head off.
74:
Do you guys always forage for food
on other worlds, Alk?
79:
No, I usually just buy everything in
Palpebra.
88:
The fruit around here is about as
good as it gets. Perfect for a special
occasion.
91: Eh, I guess we should just tell her.
94:
We're gonna throw a little party
today, Misogi, to celebrate you
reuniting with your friends.
103: Why didn't you tell me earlier?!
107:
We've still got lots of things to find,
right? I'm gonna grab as much food
as we can carry!
114:
Yay! That makes seven! No way I'm
losing now!
118:
How are you so good at this? I
haven't even caught one yet...
122:
Hehe! Actually, I modified the lure a
bit! I can use it to pull pranks, too!
126:
Oof... At this rate, you're gonna be
the only one to catch anything.
129: Ah! A bite! It feels like a big one!
153: Haha! That was kinda fun! But...
156: Are you gonna eat these monsters?
164:
Well, I do know somebody who
could make them palatable, but...
170:
I won't be having any, thank you
very much! That woman's cooking is
an affront to nature!
178:
Whoa! It's super strong! Help me out
here, Alk!
183: Geez, what is this thing? Hngh!
186:
M-Misogi! Pull hard on the count of
three!
202:
This is crazy! Are you two seeing
this?! Hahaha!
207:
Huge is right! I guess we've got a
main dish now!
211:
We've got something awesome to
brag about, too!
215:
Alk, Misogi. How's the cooking
coming along? Things are nearly
ready in the hall...
218:
Oh, my! You've got quite the
banquet prepared!
222:
We're pretty much done too. Misogi's
been a huge help.
227: I'm not so good at cooking, though.
230:
Ah, but I made those cupcakes over
there all by myself!
235: Wonderful! I cannot wait to try one—
240:
But! I made one of them
super-ultra-spicy, so choose
carefully!
249:
W-well... Perhaps this will help... liven
things up a little?
254:
Hehe, can't wait to see my victim's
face!
